<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />But I am a worm and not a man,</para>

<para style="q1">a disgrace to humanity and despised by the people.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />All those who see me taunt me;</para>

<para style="q1">they mock me; they shake their heads at me.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />They say, "He trusts in Yahweh;</para>

<para style="q1">let Yahweh rescue him.</para>

<para style="q1">Let him rescue him, for he delights in him."</para>
